I am curious, empathetic and passionate about my users.

I strive to handle problems during any stage of product development and turn them into actionable insights to provide great user experience. I am result oriented and self motivated and excellent at building relationship with business unit executives and collaborating with designers, product managers and TL engineers to drive product from planning to launch.

Specialties: 
Usability testing,
Ethnography,
Focus groups, 
Contextual inquiry, 
Validation (Inter-Operability and Co-existence Testing),
Heuristic evaluations,
Usability Testing,
Longitudinal studies,
F24 Hour studies

Strengths:
Proven collaboration with architects, engineers and planners,
Ability to synthesize data to extract actionable and tangible insights,
Developing Consumer Journey and writing functional as well as non-functional requirements for products,
Experience conducting research in international settings including Asia and United States,
Experience leading and mentoring researchers,
Being an active member of the professional and scientific community
